metadata.name: Original Banksy Morons
metadata.description: This 1 of 1 NFT was created upon the burning of the original Pest Control-certified Banksy Morons print #325 of 500. This is the first ever authentic Banksy piece being turned into an NFT. Watch the burning of the piece here: https://twitter.com/burntbanksy. View the original COA on IPFS: https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmZg8P27gs6aQTxMhd7Qha4G9xkHdar8iYSHnQSksYaWsN/original-banksy-morons-coa.jpg
